rows.label: qev085204_MSG0002
rows.name: Hey, wait a sec. Those are the jerks who were hassling Irina![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085204_SEL0011
rows.name: Say you should help them out.

rows.label: qev085204_SEL0021
rows.name: Let them deal with it themselves.

rows.label: qev085204_MSG0004
rows.name:
That's enough! Now let's get in there
and take that thing down.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085204_MSG0006
rows.name: Right? They wanted a fight so bad, and now they got one.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085204_MSG0007
rows.name: Stay here if you like, but I'm going in![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085204_MSG0010
rows.name:
A BLADE's a BLADE.
We don't abandon our comrades in the field, no matter what.[ST:wait ]
